or, J., Vonderharr, M., Production and microtopography of bog bryophytes: Response to warming and water-table manipulations (2001) Oecologia, 128, pp. 557-565","Breeuwer, A.; Nature Conservation and Plant Ecology, Department of Environmental Sciences, Wageningen University, P.O. Box 47, Wageningen 6700 AA, Netherlands; email: a.breeuwer@gmail.com",,,,,,,,00298549,,OECOB,18283501,"English","Oecologia",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-42149167896
